{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:04:46.862243+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Based on the repository contents, here is a summary of how to install, configure, and deploy this React Firebase starter to GitHub Pages.\n\n---\n\n## Installation\n\nUse the Create React App template to scaffold a new project:\n\n```bash\nnpx create-react-app your-project-name --template firebase-starter\n```\n\nor with Yarn:\n\n```bash\nyarn create react-app your-project-name --template firebase-starter\n```\n\nThis pulls the template from the `template/` directory (the actual scaffolded files live under `template/src/`, `template/public/`, and `template/.env`).\n\n---\n\n## Configuration\n\n### 1. Firebase Setup\n1. Go to the [Firebase Console](https://console.firebase.google.com/) and add a new project.\n2. Register a **Web App** and copy the Firebase SDK configuration object.\n3. Create (or edit) a **`.env`** file in the project root with the following variables (replace the placeholder values with your real Firebase config):\n\n```env\nREACT_APP_FirebaseApiKey=your-api-key\nREACT_APP_FirebaseAuthDomain=your-auth-domain\nREACT_APP_FirebaseProjectId=your-project-id\nREACT_APP_FirebaseStorageBucket=your-storage-bucket\nREACT_APP_FirebaseMessagingSenderId=your-sender-id\nREACT_APP_FirebaseAppId=your-app-id\n```\n\nThese environment variables are consumed by `src/config/firebase.config.js`:\n```js\nexport const firebaseConfig = {\n  apiKey: process.env.REACT_APP_FirebaseApiKey,\n  authDomain: process.env.REACT_APP_FirebaseAuthDomain,\n  projectId: process.env.REACT_APP_FirebaseProjectId,\n  storageBucket: process.env.REACT_APP_FirebaseStorageBucket,\n  messagingSenderId: process.env.REACT_APP_FirebaseMessagingSenderId,\n  appId: process.env.REACT_APP_FirebaseAppId,\n};\n```\n\n### 2. Enable Google Sign-In\n1. In Firebase Console → **Authentication** → **Get Started**.\n2. Under **Sign-in method**, click **Google**, toggle **Enable**, and **Save**.\n\n### 3. Prepare for GitHub Pages Deployment\n1. In Firebase Console → **Authentication** → **Sign-in method** → **Authorized domains**, add your GitHub Pages domain:  \n   `your-github-username.github.io`\n2. Update the **`homepage`** field in `package.json` to point to your hosting URL. By convention, this is:  \n   `https://your-github-username.github.io/your-repo-name`\n3. (Optional) Test the production build locally by temporarily setting `\"homepage\": \".\"` and running:\n   ```bash\n   npm run build-and-serve\n   ```\n\n---\n\n## Deploy to GitHub Pages\n\nRun the deploy script:\n\n```bash\nnpm run deploy\n```\n\nThis executes the npm scripts defined in `package.json`:\n\n```json\n\"predeploy\": \"npm run build\",\n\"deploy\": \"gh-pages -d build\"\n```\n\n- `predeploy` builds the React app into the `build/` directory.\n- `deploy` pushes that `build/` folder to the `gh-pages` branch of your repository via the `gh-pages` package (devDependency `\"gh-pages\": \"^3.2.3\"`).\n\nA `public/404.html` file (with the SPA redirect script from [`spa-github-pages`](https://github.com/rafgraph/spa-github-pages)) is included to handle client-side routing on GitHub Pages.\n\n---\n\n## Quick Reference\n\n| Step | Command / Action |\n|------|-----------------|\n| Scaffold | `npx create-react-app my-app --template firebase-starter` |\n| Firebase config | Fill `.env` with your Firebase SDK values |\n| Enable Google Auth | Firebase Console → Authentication → Google sign-in |\n| Authorize domain | Add `your-username.github.io` to Firebase Auth domains |\n| Set homepage | Edit `\"homepage\"` in `package.json` |\n| **Deploy** | **`npm run deploy`** |", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 1283, "prompt_tokens": 12888, "total_tokens": 14171, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 382, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 12288}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 12288, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 600}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-flash", "system_fingerprint": "fp_8b330d02d0_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "54aea6e1-9fa5-4f0d-b5c0-3cb598ae1077", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3e6-d4bc-7602-a2ef-26d8cf3ad4ba-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 12888, "output_tokens": 1283, "total_tokens": 14171, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 12288}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 382}}}}]}}}
